  "response": "Certainly! Below is a list of some famous soccer players along with their traditional or most recognized jersey numbers. Please note that players may have different numbers when they switch clubs or national teams.\n\n### **Lionel Messi**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **FC Barcelona:** #10\n  - **Paris Saint-Germain (PSG):** #30\n  - **Inter Miami:** #10\n- **Argentina National Team:** #10\n\n### **Cristiano Ronaldo**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Manchester United:** #7\n  - **Real Madrid:** #7\n  - **Juventus:** #7\n  - **Al Nassr:** #7\n- **Portugal National Team:** #7\n\n### **Neymar Jr.**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Santos FC:** #11\n  - **FC Barcelona:** #10\n  - **Paris Saint-Germain (PSG):** #10\n- **Brazil National Team:** #10\n\n### **Kylian Mbapp\u00e9**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **AS Monaco:** #29\n  - **Paris Saint-Germain (PSG):** #7\n- **France National Team:** #10\n\n### **Luka Modri\u0107**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Dinamo Zagreb:** #10\n  - **Tottenham Hotspur:** #10\n  - **Real Madrid:** #10\n- **Croatia National Team:** #10\n\n### **Sergio Ramos**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Sevilla FC:** #4\n  - **Real Madrid:** #4\n  - **Paris Saint-Germain (PSG):** #4\n- **Spain National Team:** #4\n\n### **Zinedine Zidane**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Bordeaux:** #10\n  - **Juventus:** #10\n  - **Real Madrid:** #5\n- **France National Team:** #10\n\n### **J\u00fcrgen Klopp**\n*(Note: Klopp is a famous manager rather than a player, but mentioning him for context)*\n- **Jersey Number:** N/A (as a manager)\n\n### **David Beckham**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Manchester United:** #7\n  - **Real Madrid:** #23\n  - **LA Galaxy:** #23\n  - **AC Milan:** #23\n  - **Paris Saint-Germain (PSG):** #23\n- **England National Team:** #23 (also wore #7 occasionally)\n\n### **Ronaldinho**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Gr\u00eamio:** #11\n  - **Paris Saint-Germain (PSG):** #10\n  - **Barcelona:** #10\n  - **AC Milan:** #10\n- **Brazil National Team:** #10\n\n### **Paolo Maldini**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **AC Milan:** #3\n- **Italy National Team:** #3\n\n### **Thierry Henry**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Monaco:** #12\n  - **Juventus:** #14\n  - **Arsenal:** #14\n  - **Barcelona:** #14\n- **France National Team:** #12 and #14\n\n### **Andr\u00e9s Iniesta**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **FC Barcelona:** #8 (later #6)\n  - **Vissel Kobe:** #6\n- **Spain National Team:** #8\n\n### **Gareth Bale**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Tottenham Hotspur:** #11\n  - **Real Madrid:** #11\n- **Wales National Team:** #11\n\n### **Mohamed Salah**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **FC Basel:** #11\n  - **Chelsea:** #11\n  - **AC Milan:** #11\n  - **Liverpool:** #11\n- **Egypt National Team:** #11\n\n### **Robert Lewandowski**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Borussia Dortmund:** #9\n  - **Bayern Munich:** #9\n  - **FC Barcelona:** #9\n- **Poland National Team:** #9\n\n### **Zlatan Ibrahimovi\u0107**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Ajax:** #10\n  - **Juventus:** #11\n  - **Inter Milan:** #9\n  - **Barcelona:** #11\n  - **AC Milan:** #10\n  - **Paris Saint-Germain (PSG):** #9\n  - **Manchester United:** #9\n  - **LA Galaxy:** #10\n- **Sweden National Team:** #9\n\n### **Eden Hazard**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Chelsea:** #10\n  - **Real Madrid:** #7\n- **Belgium National Team:** #10\n\n### **Kevin De Bruyne**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Woluwe AC:** #17\n  - **Chelsea:** #17\n  - **Werder Bremen:** #17\n  - **VfL Wolfsburg:** #17\n  - **Manchester City:** #17\n- **Belgium National Team:** #17\n\n### **Virgil van Dijk**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Ajax:** #4\n  - **Southampton:** #4\n  - **Liverpool:** #4\n- **Netherlands National Team:** #4\n\n### **Sadio Man\u00e9**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Bordeaux:** #10\n  - **Southampton:** #10\n  - **Liverpool:** #10\n  - **Bayern Munich:** #10\n  - **Al Nassr:** #10\n- **Senegal National Team:** #10\n\n### **N'Golo Kant\u00e9**\n- **Clubs:**\n  - **Boulogne:** #7\n  - **Caen:** #7\n  - **Leicester City:** #7\n  - **Chelsea:** #7\n- **France National Team:** #7\n\n---\n\n**Note:** Jersey numbers can sometimes change based on team requirements, player transfers, or personal preferences. Additionally, some players have iconic numbers associated with them throughout their careers, even if they have worn different numbers at different times.\n\nIf you have specific players in mind or need information about a particular league or era, feel free to ask!",
